responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "BAA8A39146AC93D75A4EDA9BAD7BA819", "Let\'s take it slow. I don\'t want to jump to any conclusions. They may have an intimidating name, but they\'re not usually looking for trouble. The Terrorgore are a nomadic tribe, they don\'t often stay in one place for longer than a season. Take a look around a few of their camps and come back here to tell me what you discover. I\'ll watch the gates of the Keep in the meantime.")
name: 0019_1_P1_Raaqir_65
